702638f-a.title: Brooklyn: 20th Avenue - Cropsey Avenue
702638f-a.text:
(1)
Twentieth Ave., west side, south of Cropsey Ave., showing the
''Captain's Pier.'
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(2)
The same, showing a westerly view. (Warehouse Ave. will cut
directly through the end of the pavilion on the pier when completed).
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(3)
The same, another view.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection. 1
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

702639f-a.title: Brooklyn: 20th Avenue - Cropsey Avenue
702639f-a.text:
20th Avenue (right), adjoining the N. W. corner of
Cropsey Avenue, showing the Buena Vista Hotel. The view
is up 20th Avenue across fill for the new Belt Parkway.
May 28, 1939
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
